@startuml
actor Lecturer
participant "React Client" as Client
participant "Express API" as API
participant "Auth/Role Middleware" as Auth
participant "Exam Service" as Service
database PostgreSQL as DB
participant WebSocket as WS

Lecturer -> Client : Fill exam form
Client -> API : POST /api/exams + JWT
API -> Auth : Verify teacher role
Auth --> API : Authorized
API -> Service : createExam(payload)
Service -> Service : Validate questions and points
Service -> DB : INSERT draft exam + questions JSONB
DB --> Service : Created exam
Service --> API : Exam DTO
API --> Client : 201 Created

Lecturer -> Client : Publish exam
Client -> API : PATCH /api/exams/:id/publish
API -> Service : publishExam()
Service -> DB : UPDATE status = published
Service -> WS : Broadcast exam_published
API --> Client : Published exam
@enduml
